710714f-a.title: Manhattan: 11th Avenue - 47th Street (West)
710714f-a.text:
11th Avenue, north from W. 47th Street. The hut shown in the
foreground is for the New York Central Railroad watchman and guard.
Trains at this date used the street bed.
About 1931
Views 1,2
P. L. Sperr

713307f-a.title: Manhattan: 47th Street (West) - [11th Avenue]
713307f-a.text:
